body_html:
Thanks @vrv for the review. The PR has been updated so that all invalid argument keys would be printed in case of error. A test case has been added as well.

I also updated with

   $ bazel-bin/tensorflow/tools/api/tests/api_compatibility_test \
          --update_goldens True

so that api_compatibility_test could pass on Jenkins.

Please take a look and let me know if there are any issues.

Thanks @vrv for the review. The PR has been updated so that all invalid argument keys would be printed in case of error. A test case has been added as well.

I also updated with
```
   $ bazel-bin/tensorflow/tools/api/tests/api_compatibility_test \
          --update_goldens True
```
so that api_compatibility_test could pass on Jenkins.

Please take a look and let me know if there are any issues.
